Synopsis: Imports an OAI Assistant from a JSON file.
Description: The Import-OAIAssistant function imports an OAI Assistant from a JSON file and creates a new OAI Assistant object.

Examples.Title: EXAMPLE 1
Examples.Code:
Import-OAIAssistant -Path "C:\OAIAssistant.json"
This example imports an OAI Assistant from the "C:\OAIAssistant.json" file.
